{
  "text": "In that case, I'll ask you. She stated that Ra used the tarot to develop the magical personality. Was this done in the system of learning to become in mind the essence of each archetype and in this way develop the magical personality? This is incorrect. Is an advanced practice of the adept which has long studied this archetypical system. The concept complexes which together are intended to represent the architecture of a significant and rich portion of the mind are intended to be studied as individual concept complexes as a matrix, a potentiator, etcetera, in a viewing a mind, a body, a spirit, a connections, and in affairs with some concentration upon the polarity of the male and the female. If these are studied, there comes the moment when the deep Threnodes and a joyful Odities of the Deep Mind can successfully be brought forward to intensify, articulate, and heighten some aspect of the magical personality.",
